The latter, it must be said, still has enormous deficiencies, not proposing any explanation for the gravity (ops!) or the dark matter, which forms about 80% of the matter of the Universe (re-ops!).
But no such deviations have been found at CERN so far.
Effects
The impact of these research on the daily lives of Mr. and Mrs. All-World, they are more difficult to predict, but it would be wrong to assume that there will be no such thing.
