Some people come to us with a romantic vision and head in the clouds and, when they realize that they must come to the rehearsals twice a week, follow the preparatory courses and spend a lot of time on the streets for concerts, they quickly lose their enthusiasm.
But it works the same way in each group that wants to work and achieve goals.
The Tap Tap group currently has twenty members.
