We had a good team composed of Julio Toro, Flor Meléndez, Carlos Morales, Raymond Dalmau, Armandito Torres.
In young people, I love the work Leo Arill does.
For you, what is your greatest success in the federation?
Having is part of the most glorious period of the national team between 1988 and 1995, and the fact that in the early 1990s, the NSB had up to 17 teams in one season.
What do you have to do?
There are things I would have wanted to put in place, such as the regionalization of the smaller categories.
